::Prowl::

Prowl nearly jumps as he hears Dinobot's growl. The bot's aproach had taken 
the Maximal by surprise, crashing his train-of thought. He turns to Dinobot, 
a frown on his face.

"This equipment is a bit out of date. We'll need to get to the new base to 
get what we need."

With that, Prowl walks toward the door, too occupied to wait for Dinobot's 
answer. He was trying to keep his mind off of what the Alliance might be 
doing to Iron Raptor. He clenches his teeth. If the Alliance did anything to 
the bot he loved, they would have a mean bomb in their engine room....

"Let's hurry," he says over his shoulder to Dinobot, exiting the Ark and 
flying off toward the Cybertronian Fire at full speed.
